name: Neotoma 1
notes:
Based on IntCal13 calibration curve. Based on the basal dates from the fossil insect section (Elias et al. 1991), the ages extrapolated below 175 cm are probably too old, thus the older reliable age bound is set to 10,600 cal yr BP. The age of the surface sample (0 cm) based on date of collection.

206 #d.max
1 #d.by
1 #depths.file
NA #slump
50 #acc.mean
1.5 #acc.shape

4 #mem.strength
NA #hiatus.depths
1000 #hiatus.mean
1 #hiatus.shape
0 #BCAD
1 #cc
0 #postbomb
IntCal13 #cc1
Marine13 #cc2
SHCal13 #cc3
ConstCal #cc4
cm #unit
0 #normal
3 #t.a
4 #t.b

0.95 #prob
